Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:28.10,Lyriccn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Aimo Aimo Neder Loussier
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:38.19,Lyric,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}打ち鳴らせ　今　勝利の　鐘を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:38.19,Lyriccn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}敲响如今胜利的钟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.73,Lyric,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ここは……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.73,Lyriccn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}这是……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 布雷拉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 这糖…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是糖 我说的是歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平时的那种歌声 我想听再多听一些…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.91,0:09:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时的?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.02,0:09:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在听我唱的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌让宇宙有了感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是冷漠的宇宙 而是如怀抱般…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河的漩涡就这样成形…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不出很好的比喻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 谢谢你 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是布雷拉先生…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时在格里菲斯公园遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想问你 为什么会那首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 极密事项
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人发现的话 会被骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的认为我做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的歌有那种力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.66,0:10:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 虽然听说是被老板叫去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方都讲了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是洞察力好得有些多余 米歇尔这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fold水晶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.69,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1000,964)}Quartz
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:10:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这儿干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自以为是 又不是为了来见你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 不是还没有痊愈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 快去医院…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不要去宾馆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.33,0:11:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要被关着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个救回来的女孩是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.51,0:11:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 到底干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 那 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.33,0:11:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我费了多大功夫把晕倒的你带回S.M.S
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你知道我有多担心吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你原来为我担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问我为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块石头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.13,0:12:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不要 阿露特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好把女人带回房的时候 要在门上夹块手帕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 谁会和这样的女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这样的女人」算什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你 说你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭阿露特你 也敢这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们慢慢来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 紧急召集吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有给骷髅小队的极密任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极密?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然详细内容会在作战会议传达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是李兰华 以她的歌声为实验的护卫工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的歌声会传达给Vajra 这种梦话你是当真说的?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 所以才要做实验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这事已经得到了你妹妹的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就算你嚷嚷也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华的歌声会改变Vajra的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说军队的大人物中有不少相信「Minmei Attack」的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:56.15,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Minmei Attack:即「明美作战」 第一次宇宙战争中人类通过林明美的歌声击败天顶星人的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对Vajra这样的对手 还让它们听歌 这算怎么回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对手是我们的祖先或是「原始恶魔」尚且下不了定论
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.90,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1100,964)}Protodeviln
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.90,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}原始恶魔: MACROSS 7中出现的一种宇宙生物，由原始文明所创造，\N以吸食宇宙中其他生物的精神能量为生。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况那些家伙连智慧生命都算不上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是生物 就一定有某种交流手段
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这实验成功的话 我们的战斗就会容易很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为有一试的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 卡娜丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽力平稳飞行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果感觉不适的话 请立即告知我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 拜托了卡娜丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你自己的愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 绝对不要出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果露馅的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髅1号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将与新统合军Galaxy的特别派遣 VF27小队会合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小队长的识别信号为 天蝎1号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.30,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1194,964)}Antares
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷拉·斯坦少校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会以这样的形式与那架机体并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊? 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上1级警戒的舰桥可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得允许过你登船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能说明一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这机密任务的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容和目的也都听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在威胁我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 怀尔德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我把这一切看到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是固执
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给她安排座位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会一切顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连麦克风和扬声器都没使用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何让那些家伙听到歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那个女孩的歌声中检测到了微弱的Fold波
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说理由不明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这种随便的理由而动用了如此多的人员和器材?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有能确认这现象 就有使用的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不就是这样走到今天这一步的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quarter 到达预定实验宙域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到「巢穴」编号 Alpha-121号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ranka Attack 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们发动先攻 把Vajra轰出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特他们的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天蝎1号 为什么不行动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们自己参与进去的话 就不是做实验了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华小姐 请开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情指数 ＋4.33
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fold Wave  Level3.2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华 你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra的行动变得不规则 攻击停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到 是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天蝎1号已确认效果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始肃敌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.54,0:19:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 不要落后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你们溜掉的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不是你死就是我亡的话 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情指数…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.49,0:20:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还需要不断调教呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 骷髅4号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷拉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:20:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷拉 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:21:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就说过了 你不适合那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 能赢 这样我们就能赢得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了 兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像传说中的明美哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.17,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}明美：初代Macross中的女主角林明美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太老了 这样说的话应该是巴萨拉大人才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:39.14,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}巴萨拉:Macross7的男主角 用歌声终止了人类与原始恶魔的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也够老了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华昂首挺胸 现在你是寄托了我们希望的歌姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.47,0:21:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超时空灰姑娘 魅惑的歌姬 就是兰华你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 说得太过了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.86,0:22:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样…这样…是对的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.59,0:23:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是年轻时的奥兹马对自己所许下的唯一的誓言
